http.title: Online Services 1
http.html:
Welcome to the Forestry Commission Online Business Services

Here you can access our Timber Online Sales Service to purchase standing timber via online auction.

You can also access our range of Grant and Licence Online Services, which allow you to:

  • G&L Online Service. - to make a grant application online.
    Please note : The English Woodland Grant Scheme has now closed for any new applications.
  • Land Information Search - to search on a chosen area for land designations and features.
  • Register of Grant Scheme and Felling Applications - to view applications for grants felling licence applications.
  • Register of Environmental Impact Assessment - to view details of the decisions that we make after our assessment of the potential environmental impact of forestry products.

GLOS is now only available as read only for our external Forestry Commission Customers. We apologise for any inconvenience that this may cause. Please note that external GLOS users will no longer be able to use the online GLOS system to raise claims. If you have any queries please contact gr.support.england@forestry.gsi.gov.uk
